Understanding of the responsibilities of an IT professional and the ethical, social, and legal issues related to computing.', '否', '是', '否', 'https://www.comp.nus.edu.sg/programmes/ug/cs/curr', 'https://www.comp.nus.edu.sg/about/faculty/', NULL);
